        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Down the Debt Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill rescinds appropriations that were provided for grants that were not accepted by a state or local government. The rescinded funds must be deposited in the Treasury and used for deficit reduction.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
